data.description: Like new, beautiful  single story home available to call home. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath + den, that could be used as an additional bedroom, offers all the best features: high ceilings, gourmet kitchen, huge island, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and timeless tile flooring throughout. Open floor plan with great room, dining area and split bedroom plan. In front of the home is an extra long driveway leading into a 2 car garage. In the back is a covered patio with concrete pad and level lot with plenty of room to enjoy. Easy to see. Call/text for your showing today!
